                          <div class="c-Main__body-abt__desc">
                              Rishika Pillai is currently a senior at Coppell High School. She has been learning Bharatanatyam since the age of five, and it has grown to become one of her most heartfelt passions. Rishika has completed the Senior Certificate in Bharatanatyam from the SAMPADA SiliconAndhra Organization with distinction and spends her free time teaching dance to students at Natyom. She has also been learning Carnatic Music from Smt. Latha Varadarajan. Outside of dance, Rishika likes to read books, watch movies, listen to music and spend time with her friends and family. She plans on attending college in the fall.
